skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: stream sounds
des: What better way to fall asleep than to a small stream winding through the wilderness. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Stream Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
